        "body": "<p>There's a special type for this kind of computation called <code>BigInteger<\/code>. Find more infos <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/math/BigInteger.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n<p><strong>Edit:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<p>You can create a <code>BigInteger<\/code> from a <code>String<\/code><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>BigInteger bigInt = new BigInteger(\"24\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or from an integer type<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>BigInteger fromInt = BigInteger.valueOf(24);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
